  <input type="button" onclick="alert('its okay to feel angry at times. take a break and relax. practice healthy coping mechanisms such as deep breathing, meditation, and journaling. accept whats out of your control. take a time out and think before you speak. dont let the anger consume you.')" value="angry"')" />
  
